Third Department,

September, 1954.

(September 15, 1954.) In the Matter of the Claim of Rose Bittetto, Appellant, against Gruenstein & Mayer et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

. Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default, without costs. Present — Foster, P. J., Bergan, Coon, Halpern and Imrie, JJ.
